1. Input items - Post
- Route: /inputItems
Method: POST
sample payload:
```json
[
    {
        "name" : "onion",
        "quantity" : 1000,
        "unit" : "grams"
    },
    {
        "name" : "potato",
        "quantity" : 2000,
        "unit" : "grams"
    },
    {
        "name" : "chicken",
        "quantity" : 2000,
        "unit" : "grams"
    }
]

2. Add item - Post
- Route: /addItem
Method: POST
sample payload:
```json
{
    "name" : "onion",
    "quantity" : 1000,
    "unit" : "grams"
}


3. Update item after shopping
- Route: /updateItem
Method: PUT
sample payload:
```json
{
    "name" : "onion",
    "purchased_quantity" : 1000,
    "unit" : "grams"
}



4. Add raw recipe text
- Route: /addRawRecipeText
Method: POST
sample payload:
```json
{
    "dish_name" : "onion soup",
    "description" : "warm comforting soup made with onion chicken and lots of pepper. Give proper amount of salt and chili. Takes your like to peel and chop the onions to little pieces. Cook the chicke to perfection, it requires 20 minutes to cook a perfect chicken. Simmer all the ingredients except chicken, add the chicken after 10 minutes. You are good to go"
}



